# Downloaded bug-report replays and scripts/replay-to-gif.js's generated GIF/viewer output --
# investigation artifacts for a specific report (the GitHub issue is the source of truth), not
# source code. Kept out of git so the repo doesn't accumulate binary blobs per investigation, but
# living in-tree (not a job-scoped tmp dir) so they're a durable, easy-to-find local location
# instead of disappearing when a session/job is cleaned up.
replays/
